textAnnotations.description:
A PLAYER TO BE
NAMED LATER
Featuring
BRAD TYLER, MICAN FRANKLIN, KYLE PETERSON and MARCO SCUTARO
This film reminds us of the best of baseball - the sport behind the
business, the human drama behind the game, and the dedication
and dreams of those who play the game. It's an odds-on favorite
to be a hitr - USA TODAY'S Danny Sheridan
DVD
